There is a lot of other work under the brand Victor of Valencia, and I feel a draw to show you what else I do. At the end of the day, we are artists and creators, and as a freelance photographer, my work extends into multiple realms. Love y’all. Lots of cool stuff on the way! @kosas and Vert Beauty featured.
